ibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:375\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.375</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; later <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἶ. βιησάμενος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0221.tlg001:90\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Euph.\">Euph.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">90</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc.—Freq. in prop. names, e.g. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἰφιάνασσα, Ἰφιγένεια, Ἰφιγόνη, Ἰφιδάμας, Ἴφικλος, ϝιφιάδας</foreign>, etc.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}